WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.240 --> 00:00:01.679
Well, good evening, family.

00:00:01.679 --> 00:00:03.943
Thank you for joining me again today.

00:00:03.943 --> 00:00:10.116
We're going to go over some of the things the Lord showed us in this last video three days ago.

00:00:10.951 --> 00:00:17.520
I've taken some time to pray over what the Lord has been showing me.

00:00:17.520 --> 00:00:23.780
Some of the things, like I always talk to you all about, is knowing your audience.

00:00:23.780 --> 00:00:36.640
Now, what the Lord has been showing me the last 48 hours really strong is concerning the leadership in the church.

00:00:40.719 --> 00:00:40.959
Everybody's a leader in the body of Christ.

00:00:44.914 --> 00:00:45.800
You're leading somebody.

00:00:45.800 --> 00:00:49.120
There's always somebody watching.

00:00:49.120 --> 00:01:01.150
But whenever God puts his hand on you to lead as a pastor, teacher, evangelist, or prophetic voice, too much is given, much is required.

00:01:05.952 --> 00:01:24.149
As I was praying, the word has been very heavy to the point where I didn't want to come across making a video last night as fear.

00:01:24.159 --> 00:01:33.200
I want to be precise in how I'm saying things so that you can take it to God in prayer.

00:01:33.200 --> 00:01:44.266
Everything I say is my opinion of what the Holy Spirit is showing me and what I feel the Lord is leading me in prayer to.

00:01:44.266 --> 00:01:51.600
Right now, he's examining his troops.

00:01:52.010 --> 00:01:55.634
He told me, 'I'm examining my leadership.

00:01:55.634 --> 00:01:58.040
I'm examining the troops.

00:01:58.040 --> 00:02:25.093
' He started talking to me about how all the children of Israel, because there was doubt and unbelief in them, that generation didn't get to go on and experience the promise because they said, 'We're the size of grasshoppers.

00:02:25.093 --> 00:02:31.720
' They didn't go and inherit the land because they were afraid.

00:02:41.920 --> 00:02:47.600
They didn't do what God had called them to do.

00:02:49.130 --> 00:03:02.320
So, a whole generation had to pass away, other than just a handful, to go and take the promised land, Canaan—the beautiful milk and honey—but the giants were in the land, right?

00:03:06.959 --> 00:03:26.862
As I was praying, he was relaying that there's a lot of elders and people that are in ministry right now where there's going to be a real reshaping of the body of Christ.

00:03:34.240 --> 00:03:38.480
He's talking about the body of Christ as a whole.

00:03:39.008 --> 00:03:48.994
A lot of times, as charismatics, we think because we're baptized in the Holy Ghost and we walk with the giftings, he's really talking about us, but he's talking about everybody.

00:03:53.200 --> 00:03:56.606
He said, 'I'm shaking the church to awaken the church.

00:03:56.606 --> 00:04:07.724
' The church isn't just charismatics; the church is the body of Christ—everybody.

00:04:10.640 --> 00:04:20.319
He started talking to me about Rome back 1,500 or 2,000 years ago, back when Jesus was on the earth.

00:04:30.571 --> 00:04:40.937
If you were to tell them then that Rome would cease to exist in the way they were, they would have laughed at you.

00:04:40.937 --> 00:04:43.200
Nobody is more powerful than Rome.

00:04:43.200 --> 00:04:47.840
Their army, their bridges, their roads, their infrastructure is superb.

00:04:57.680 --> 00:05:04.150
But that Rome and that power doesn't exist anymore.

00:05:04.411 --> 00:05:12.150
There's a changing of the tide and a changing of things coming.

00:05:12.160 --> 00:05:14.103
There's a shaking to awaken.

00:05:14.103 --> 00:05:24.400
There's a new financial system that's about to be rebirthed, a new global digital currency.

00:05:24.800 --> 00:05:34.920
The United States of America, over the last 100 years plus, has been the top dog in the schoolyard.

00:05:35.730 --> 00:05:43.600
You look at the United States and they're the supreme military, the best of everything.

00:05:43.600 --> 00:05:55.120
But for the first time ever, I saw military things taking place on our own home soil.

00:05:55.120 --> 00:06:04.080
Not a civil war per se, but an actual invasion like a Trojan horse.

00:06:04.080 --> 00:06:16.309
I keep seeing this 'enemy within,' and I saw a wounded eagle.

00:06:16.319 --> 00:06:26.578
I saw this wounded eagle, this wounded bird; the dove that was laying had trusted in that.

00:06:26.826 --> 00:06:34.020
I saw the dove with two black crows and a beautiful cardinal that took the dove's heart.

00:06:34.020 --> 00:06:48.560
I saw a dove of peace dead on the ground, and I saw the heart that was ripped out of the dove by the two black crows.

00:06:48.830 --> 00:06:57.840
The Lord has been talking to me about the church and the shaking of this nation.

00:06:58.416 --> 00:07:02.880
As he said, 'the eyes of the Lord run to and fro.

00:07:02.880 --> 00:07:08.383
' He brought up the scripture 2 Chronicles 16:9.

00:07:08.383 --> 00:07:32.900
'For the eyes of the Lord run to and fro throughout the whole earth to show himself strong on behalf of those whose heart is loyal to him.

00:07:32.900 --> 00:07:47.120
In this you may have done foolishly; therefore, from now on you shall have wars.

00:07:47.120 --> 00:07:53.960
' As I was looking, he was examining his troops, his bride, and his leadership.

00:07:55.000 --> 00:07:59.463
He started talking to me about the shaking to awaken.

00:07:59.463 --> 00:08:15.775
From Psalm 17:8: 'Keep me as the apple of thy eye; hide me under the shadow of thy wings.

00:08:15.775 --> 00:08:23.093
' As he's examining you, he's examining the hearts.

00:08:35.909 --> 00:08:48.560
There was so much compromise and mixture in the hearts over the body of Christ, and he was calling for a pure bride to come to his side, calling forth the church to wake up out of this slumber.

00:08:59.449 --> 00:09:10.160
Psalm 17:8: 'Keep me as the apple of thy eye; hide me under the shadow of thy wings.

00:09:10.160 --> 00:09:18.240
' That's where we all should be, examining our hearts that we are the apple of his eye.

00:09:21.600 --> 00:09:31.760
2 Chronicles 16:9: 'The eye of the Lord is running to and fro looking at the hearts.

00:09:31.760 --> 00:09:39.680
' This was my heart's cry as I was praying this out and travailing in the spirit.

00:09:39.680 --> 00:09:43.200
I come to Psalm 17:8.

00:09:43.200 --> 00:10:06.000
As his eyes were gazing upon us, what does he see in you and me as leaders, like you're blowing the horn on the wall warning of the second coming of Jesus?

00:10:10.080 --> 00:10:11.520
We're all looking for the rapture.

00:10:11.520 --> 00:10:22.628
We're about to experience the greatest outpouring and move of the Spirit of the Lord we've ever seen, and many people don't believe.

00:10:24.279 --> 00:10:32.079
Can we take the land for Jesus in Cuba, Venezuela, Brazil, Thailand, South Korea, or North Korea?

00:10:45.360 --> 00:10:52.560
As I told you, there were highways in the spirit realm that we would translate.

00:10:52.560 --> 00:11:01.120
You'll be preaching in one area and then all of a sudden be translated to another area, and God will have us minister to a group of people.

00:11:04.740 --> 00:11:28.620
But taking that doubt and unbelief of the old generation because they've never seen it before—he said, 'I'm examining my troops, and there'll be some of them that will not make it to what I've called them to in this next promised land, to this revival.

00:11:28.620 --> 00:11:37.839
' I'm done with the tongue that is against—if you're not for him, you're against him.

00:11:37.839 --> 00:11:44.880
If you're not going to start saying out your mouth, we're going to have the greatest revival this world has ever seen.

00:11:44.880 --> 00:11:49.040
And I saw new young Davids; I saw new young Esthers.

00:12:03.804 --> 00:12:19.620
And he started saying, 'I heard it so loud: "If I perish, I perish.

00:12:21.680 --> 00:12:23.936
If I perish, I perish.

00:12:23.936 --> 00:12:31.519
"' When Mordecai said to Esther, 'Haven't you been called to the kingdom for such a time as this?

00:12:35.839 --> 00:12:41.013
Haven't you been called to the kingdom for such a time as this?

00:12:41.013 --> 00:12:43.977
' And he said, 'I'm examining the hearts.

00:12:43.977 --> 00:12:53.269
Is there fear in it to what I've asked you to do?

00:12:53.279 --> 00:12:57.910
Who is on the Lord's side?

00:12:57.920 --> 00:13:04.070
' I know it’s about knowing my audience, and that's why I was praying over there.

00:13:04.070 --> 00:13:07.074
I said, 'Who is on the Lord's side?

00:13:07.074 --> 00:13:22.080
' because the babies don't get it, but you veterans understand what I'm talking about.

00:13:35.279 --> 00:13:36.880
And I saw a cleansing coming of older, huge ministries—mega-ministries that have TV programs, staffs of many people, and a transition.

00:13:49.680 --> 00:13:50.056
And he said, 'Some of these will not even exist in the months ahead.

00:13:50.056 --> 00:13:57.600
For some of these, their time has come; their season is over.

00:13:57.600 --> 00:14:08.399
' And you will see one that was be no more, and one that wasn't be.

00:14:08.399 --> 00:14:18.304
And I saw a rising up of new faces that will come out of nowhere.

00:14:36.320 --> 00:14:36.686
And I saw them taking the land.

00:14:43.240 --> 00:14:45.187
I saw a bulldog faith coming on people that just say, 'If I perish, I perish.

00:14:45.187 --> 00:14:47.787
' They're not worried about themselves.

00:14:47.787 --> 00:14:50.491
They're not worried about the finances.

00:14:50.491 --> 00:14:51.634
They're not worried about what people think.

00:14:51.634 --> 00:15:05.634
He said, 'I'll raise up people to fund this with creative ideas to get wealth, to fund this end-time move.

00:15:05.634 --> 00:15:16.520
' And the Lord said, 'Brandon, there's not enough preparation in the heart.

00:15:16.520 --> 00:15:19.840
There's not enough going higher.

00:15:19.840 --> 00:15:36.285
' I saw so many eagles that were plucking with the chickens, and I was one of them.

00:15:36.285 --> 00:15:37.970
He was correcting me.

00:15:37.970 --> 00:15:42.519
He said, 'You think too much about what other people think.

00:15:42.519 --> 00:15:56.720
If you want to be a mouthpiece in this next wave, you've got to fly above all this Christian turbulence and be set apart.

00:15:56.720 --> 00:16:01.573
There's no compromise in this—no worrying about what sister clipboard thinks.

00:16:01.573 --> 00:16:05.519
Who cares what sister clipboard thinks or brother busybody?

00:16:05.519 --> 00:16:07.429
Just fly like an eagle.

00:16:18.320 --> 00:16:18.933
An eagle doesn't care about what those other chickens are doing; he's looking at them as prey.

00:16:18.933 --> 00:16:23.840
I mean, that's what an eagle usually does.

00:16:23.840 --> 00:16:30.720
But it's time to come up higher.

00:16:30.720 --> 00:16:41.508
I'm not saying we're eating our own; that's probably a bad illustration.

00:16:41.508 --> 00:16:44.200
But he's looking for snakes.

00:16:51.959 --> 00:16:52.299
An eagle is looking for the serpent.

00:16:52.299 --> 00:17:03.920
An eagle's looking for the rattlesnake, the cobra, or whatever he can do to pluck its head and eat it.

00:17:03.920 --> 00:17:05.839
That's a better illustration.

00:17:19.519 --> 00:17:19.839
You like that one?

00:17:22.193 --> 00:17:22.445
That's better.

00:17:28.400 --> 00:17:32.785
I like that.

00:17:39.474 --> 00:17:48.133
The eagle's looking for his lunch, but he's not down on the bottom plucking away like a chicken.

00:18:01.404 --> 00:18:01.787
The chicken doesn't know what's coming.

00:18:01.787 --> 00:18:09.733
An eagle does because he's up high enough to see what's coming.

00:18:18.044 --> 00:18:18.240
And as we are praying over this nation, just as Rome fell, America will be humbled.

00:18:18.240 --> 00:18:22.300
America will be humbled and shaken to awaken.

00:18:22.300 --> 00:18:25.497
We have a window of opportunity.

00:18:25.497 --> 00:18:29.467
We're praying for our president in this opportunity.

00:18:48.320 --> 00:18:48.676
As he said, 'Don't be an ostrich that sticks its head in the sand.

00:18:48.676 --> 00:18:52.240
' We become so complacent with time.

00:18:52.240 --> 00:19:16.582
Yesterday's news—we can hear about something major that happened, like a Charlie Kirk thing or whatever, and something huge happens back last year—but a lot of people go back to their Monday through Friday.

00:19:16.582 --> 00:19:30.206
They've got their nose to the grindstone, and they're going with all their heart just trying to make it and barely getting by.

00:19:47.760 --> 00:19:47.973
You get distracted with the water that's getting hotter and hotter all around you.

00:19:49.039 --> 00:19:54.231
And that's what he was talking to me about.

00:20:03.333 --> 00:20:03.564
I saw something that didn't make my flesh happy.

00:20:03.564 --> 00:20:07.496
And he's looking for the people that will say, 'If I perish, I perish.

00:20:07.496 --> 00:20:08.189
I'm sold out.

00:20:08.189 --> 00:20:09.783
' It's easy to be a parrot.

00:20:25.050 --> 00:20:25.460
I was listening to a sermon—I won't say which one—and it was really good.

00:20:25.460 --> 00:20:27.099
It blessed me.

00:20:27.099 --> 00:20:51.429
Everything the individual was saying was about fire, talking about the glory, but afterward they said, 'We're going to lay hands on people at the end of the service and we're going to experience this, right?

00:20:51.429 --> 00:20:57.679
' And it was like touching a cold stove.

00:21:07.088 --> 00:21:07.456
I watched as there was no manifestation of what the individual preached.

00:21:07.456 --> 00:21:15.211
They were so excited and enthusiastic, and the sermon tried to stir everybody up.

00:21:16.217 --> 00:21:23.429
It was one of those where you go, but there was no demonstration after the sermon was over.

00:21:23.429 --> 00:21:30.080
As I watched, the Lord said, 'I want you to see something.

00:21:30.080 --> 00:21:34.480
' He said, 'This comes out of refiner's fire.

00:21:34.480 --> 00:21:40.159
This level of glory—find the scripture—for the greater glory comes by the refining.

00:21:59.760 --> 00:22:00.053
It comes by the refining, and the greater the suffering, the greater the glory and the manifestation of the glory.

00:22:00.053 --> 00:22:07.840
' And he said it's on individuals like it was William Seymour, like it was Smith Wigglesworth.

00:22:07.840 --> 00:22:18.331
I asked why it was on these men, and it was the refining fire—'If I perish, I perish.

00:22:18.331 --> 00:22:27.040
' Like Esther, like what she said, there's a key to it.

00:22:41.680 --> 00:22:42.080
We can parrot a lot of things and we can say some things that some other elders say because it sounds good.

00:22:51.629 --> 00:22:52.099
We can stir up the crowd, and people start hooting and hollering.

00:22:52.099 --> 00:23:02.339
But there's a level of the glory, a level of the manifested presence of God that I'm after.

00:23:02.339 --> 00:23:06.960
I was listening to the parrot of the sermon.

00:23:06.960 --> 00:23:19.306
You walk away and they're saying, 'Oh, we're going to have fire in here afterward and the glory of God's going to show.

00:23:19.306 --> 00:23:24.480
' And it was like touching a cold stove.

00:23:24.480 --> 00:23:28.596
You walk away and you go, 'Was that it?

00:23:28.596 --> 00:23:40.040
' That sermon lasted for over an hour and a half, and that was the glory?

00:23:40.040 --> 00:23:42.933
Does that make sense?

00:23:42.933 --> 00:23:44.799
From suffering to glory.

00:23:52.969 --> 00:24:00.192
For I consider that the sufferings of this present time are not worthy to be compared with the glory which shall be revealed in us, Romans 8.

00:24:14.390 --> 00:24:15.020
For I consider that the sufferings of this present time are not worthy to be compared with the glory which shall be revealed in us.

00:24:15.020 --> 00:24:19.131
It comes with the glory.

00:24:19.131 --> 00:24:21.577
The greater outpouring comes with pressure.

00:24:23.787 --> 00:24:24.587
He's not going to share His glory with anyone.

00:24:46.159 --> 00:24:46.391
But I saw as you go vertical, you attract to deflect.

00:24:48.823 --> 00:24:50.650
You attract to deflect as you're that mirror, and you're always shining it up to Him.

00:24:51.386 --> 00:24:53.120
It's the reflection of the mirror.

00:24:57.872 --> 00:24:59.696
As people are looking at you, you always point them to the Father.

00:24:59.696 --> 00:25:08.605
It's the level of what I saw coming, that He's raising up new voices and new faces in what's about to happen.

00:25:08.605 --> 00:25:19.467
But the church that we've always known is going to change in a major way in the days ahead.

00:25:19.467 --> 00:25:28.347
You'll pinch yourself and even look back and say, 'I remember when,' for how we've done church in the past will be no more.

00:25:28.347 --> 00:25:33.382
We're going to do something new that's never been done before.

00:25:37.040 --> 00:25:37.360
It will be fueled by fire.

00:25:50.151 --> 00:25:50.435
It will be fueled by prayer.

00:25:50.435 --> 00:25:53.164
Ignited by His Spirit.

00:26:09.840 --> 00:26:10.320
No.

00:26:26.267 --> 00:26:26.480
What did Brother Hagin say?

00:26:26.480 --> 00:26:28.053
'Ignited with His glory.

00:26:28.053 --> 00:26:30.684
' Yeah, Ignited with His glory.

00:26:30.684 --> 00:26:32.213
Filled by fire.

00:26:32.213 --> 00:26:39.120
Tell me what it is in the comments section.

00:26:39.120 --> 00:26:46.850
But what the Lord was showing me was it's going to be fueled by prayer.

00:27:01.227 --> 00:27:04.000
And the Lord was showing me about the igniting and the last outpouring will be something that we've never seen before—where it's coming from and us being bold.

00:27:06.159 --> 00:27:07.588
Are we the size of grasshoppers in these giants' eyes?

00:27:07.588 --> 00:27:09.257
Can Cuba be saved?

00:27:09.257 --> 00:27:11.800
Can Venezuela be saved?

00:27:11.800 --> 00:27:14.970
Can we see LA be saved?

00:27:14.970 --> 00:27:17.428
Can we see Portland, Oregon have a major revival?

00:27:17.428 --> 00:27:25.810
Can we see Chicago—in the hood and the ghetto of Chicago—have a move of God?

00:27:25.810 --> 00:27:38.293
Can Chicago be touched with the fire of the Holy Ghost, with the Bloods and the Crips and the gang members?

00:27:38.293 --> 00:27:51.039
Can we see the greatest move of God in Brooklyn, in the worst parts of New York?

00:27:51.039 --> 00:27:58.980
Is it Harlem?

00:28:08.310 --> 00:28:10.251
What is it?

00:28:10.251 --> 00:28:11.097
I don't know.

00:28:11.097 --> 00:28:11.713
Skid Row.

00:28:11.713 --> 00:28:14.880
Can God come in and shake Skid Row?

00:28:14.880 --> 00:28:18.672
Oh no, we're the size of grasshoppers.

00:28:18.672 --> 00:28:25.200
That's when he said, 'I'm it.

00:28:25.200 --> 00:28:34.640
' He's killing that in people as he's examining us and he was showing me it's time for us to wake up.

00:28:34.640 --> 00:28:39.519
And that's what he's been dealing with me about.

00:28:39.519 --> 00:28:42.880
It was heavy.

00:28:42.880 --> 00:28:58.340
And as I was in deep prayer over this, he started to say, 'Brandon, I have to do something different because I'm out of time.

00:28:58.340 --> 00:29:06.836
And I'm raising up people that are on fire for me, that are just sold out, that say, "If I perish, I perish.

00:29:06.836 --> 00:29:08.465
"' You're not afraid of death.

00:29:08.465 --> 00:29:10.040
You're not afraid of that.

00:29:10.040 --> 00:29:18.800
Because I was looking at it, I said, 'Lord, we see people dying.

00:29:18.800 --> 00:29:20.240
We see this happening.

00:29:20.240 --> 00:29:24.960
' I watched Private Ryan for Memorial Day and it's a very bloody movie.

00:29:24.960 --> 00:29:27.817
I'd never seen it before, but I was doing it.

00:29:42.559 --> 00:29:43.135
It was on my heart.

00:30:03.800 --> 00:30:04.190
And you say, 'Well, Brandon, you think God told you to watch Private Ryan?

00:30:04.190 --> 00:30:09.770
' It's about honoring the troops that fell on the beaches of Normandy.

00:30:27.991 --> 00:30:40.570
As I saw them take that beach and the Germans were beating them down with those bullets and they were just shredding their bodies with stuff, and I watched them men fight as they were going up that hill to get that, I thought, 'My God, what did they fight for?

00:30:40.570 --> 00:30:50.520
' They fought for us to have freedom to be able to do what we're doing right now.

00:30:50.520 --> 00:31:12.583
They fought for us to have freedom for religion, to be able to have our Bill of Rights to do the things that we need right now for revival that's about to happen.

00:31:12.583 --> 00:31:14.895
And I'm telling you, ladies and gentlemen, it takes...

00:31:22.160 --> 00:31:22.400
people are so limp-wristed.

00:31:22.400 --> 00:31:23.720
You're so metrosexual.

00:31:23.720 --> 00:31:31.929
Skinny jeans and fog machines, and you can't tell if you're homosexual, if you're really a male.

00:31:31.929 --> 00:31:38.186
Do you have what it takes to be that bulldog on a bone?

00:31:38.186 --> 00:31:43.927
Or are you just going to be limp-wristed, sir?

00:31:43.927 --> 00:31:49.073
You're going to have to have some testosterone up in here.

00:31:49.779 --> 00:31:54.910
And we're going to have to be like the mighty men of war with David.

00:32:00.700 --> 00:32:00.910
And there's so many people that have no...

00:32:00.910 --> 00:32:07.253
well, you know, I'm just like, 'Get out of my way.

00:32:07.253 --> 00:32:13.372
' I'll never be friends.

00:32:13.372 --> 00:32:22.390
Don't ever try to talk to me.

00:32:22.390 --> 00:32:24.480
Either you got it or you don't.

00:32:24.480 --> 00:32:29.840
Either you want to fight for what God has given us or we're going to lose it.

00:32:29.840 --> 00:32:38.149
Let me give you an example of why I'm as radical inside tonight than I've ever been before.

00:32:49.817 --> 00:32:50.068
I want to read this.

00:32:50.068 --> 00:32:51.013
Move over, baby.

00:32:58.907 --> 00:32:59.209
I can't see it.

00:32:59.209 --> 00:33:00.418
Fueled by prayer.

00:33:00.418 --> 00:33:02.187
Fired by the spirit.

00:33:02.187 --> 00:33:07.039
Ignited with the glory.

00:33:07.039 --> 00:33:08.266
Fueled by prayer.

00:33:08.266 --> 00:33:10.840
Fired by the spirit.

00:33:10.840 --> 00:33:13.479
Ignited with his glory.

00:33:13.479 --> 00:33:18.773
